works.description:
The copyrighted work, which was clearly
stolen by the violating party, is a computer image designed and
distributed by me. The image was from created from stock images that
were paid for and licensed and the violating website had no rights or
licenses to use it. I would like for the content to be removed
immediately, and all or any action to the content to be halted. The
webmaster is incapable of being reached so the matter could not be
solved previous to this complaint.
